Class BetaSnake

java.lang.Object
ai.nettogrof.battlesnake.snakes.AbstractSnakeAI

Direct Known Subclasses:
JustTurnSnake, LeftSnake, RightSnake
public class BetaSnake
extends AbstractTreeSearchSnakeAI
Beta snake. This class is the "Nessegrev-Beta" snake on Battlesnake. This snake was in the Summer League/Veteran Division. Still active on the global arena. Based on the Alpha snake, but fewer bugs and a bit quicker. Decent snake using minimax/payoff matrix algorithm only. This snake can play standard, squad, and royale. This snake should work with API v0 and API v1. All the move calculation are based on API v0, and if it's API v1, then the snake switch UP and DOWN response.
Version:
Spring 2021
Author:
carl.lajeunesse
